# Quantitative Results

All quantitative tables are available in the paper and supplementary material. The project page focuses on the method overview and qualitative evidence.

# Conclusion

Bridge integrates causal inference into VFM-based DGOD with a lightweight, plug-and-play module. Across ground-level and aerial benchmarks, varied weather, and visual styles, it consistently improves robustness and generalization. The new weather-annotated UAV benchmark and supplemental analyses further broaden DG evaluation in remote sensing.
